==English==
===Etymology===
* compound [[house]] + [[sit]], formed by analogy to [[babysit]]
===Pronunciation===
(''Canada'') {{IPA|ˈhaʊsˌsɪt/}}

===Verb===
{{en-verb|house-sits|house-sitting|house-sat}}
